declarations.comments:
```purescript
app ∷ ∀msg state effs. {
    init ∷ Tuple state (Action state effs),
    view ∷ state → Document msg,
    update ∷ msg → Action state effs,
    subscriptions ∷ state → Array (Sub msg)
} → App effs
```
declarations.title: app

declarations.comments:

```purescript
    view ∷ state → VDom msg,
    update ∷ msg → state → state
} → Effect Unit
```
